{"tid":623390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京考慮貶值人民幣，連登仔又有機會北上救國啦","createTime":"2018-04-10T03:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T07:18:45.000Z","uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"233d057dfbddbce650ed0c7c476ccb1989db0f47","tid":623390,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:10:14.000Z","msg":"彭博：北京考慮貶值人民幣　回敬美貿易戰<br />\r\n財經媒體彭博引述消息人士說法報導，中國正考慮推動人民幣漸進貶值，作為回應中美貿易爭端的手段。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n消息人士透露，中國官員正對2方面進行評估分析，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">第1是以人民幣匯率作為貿易談判工具的有效性；第2是透過貶抑人民幣來抵銷任何可能限制出口的貿易協議影響，將有何後果</span></strong>。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n荷蘭國際集團（ING）駐倫敦策略師Viraj Patel說：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「這看來像是北京在全面展現能用於回應川普保護主義衝擊的政策。」</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2e122d7461881519bd01c10d76ea1b65cb782e82","tid":623390,"uid":169116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:14:57.000Z","msg":"人仔貶值咪外匯流出跟手金融市場PK囉,上年咪試過囉."},{"pid":"efa1b25ed1786b129340094cd416f8f830cd6b3b","tid":623390,"uid":15815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:17:48.000Z","msg":"強迫有錢佬成副身家兌晒人仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係時候報國la"},{"pid":"cfc1aba9f25278cd23f026c0f7dd381830ed6143","tid":623390,"uid":26752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:29:38.000Z","msg":"支那雞不了<br />\n要救不如救下班烏克蘭妹啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948eb778f8fd84845e658f8df3032687701fabd0","tid":623390,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:35:03.000Z","msg":"要幾多大陸婆做雞先掂<br />\n成千億美金逆差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d288564fff8f626377fdd549908ba54b4df72e","tid":623390,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T06:29:04.000Z","msg":"又可以睇下大陸個市幾分鐘跌到停牌"},{"pid":"766b5e7c5f180e1c635c9f728d2d53b61b5407e0","tid":623390,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r